---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <div class="ad-test-container">
        <h1>Google Ads Testing Page</h1>
        <p>This is a private page for testing Google Ads. Not for public consumption.</p>

        <!-- Ad Test Container -->
        <div class="ad-container">
            <h2>Display Ad Test</h2>
            <ins
                class="adsbygoogle"
                style="display:block"
                data-ad-client="ca-pub-7606819328826318"
                data-ad-slot="9525295321"
                data-ad-format="auto"
                data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
            <script>
                (window.adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
            </script>
        </div>

        <!-- Another Ad Test Container -->
        <div class="ad-container">
            <h2>In-article Ad Test</h2>
            <div class="article-content">
                <p>
                    This is sample article content to test in-article ads. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur
                    adipiscing elit. Mauris feugiat turpis vel eros euismod feugiat. Nullam nec nisl eu urna tincidunt
                    feugiat.
                </p>

                <ins
                    class="adsbygoogle"
                    style="display:block; text-align:center;"
                    data-ad-layout="in-article"
                    data-ad-format="fluid"
                    data-ad-client="ca-pub-7606819328826318"
                    data-ad-slot="5960011875"></ins>
                <script>
                    (window.adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
                </script>

                <p>
                    More sample content after the ad. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices
                    posuere cubilia curae; Sed at condimentum eros. Integer sed lacus et nisi vestibulum eleifend.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="instructions">
            <h3>How to use this page:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Replace "YOUR_AD_SLOT_ID" with your actual Google Ad slot IDs</li>
                <li>Test different ad formats and placements on this page</li>
                <li>Monitor performance in your Google AdSense dashboard</li>
            </ol>
            <p>This page is intentionally not indexed by search engines to keep it private.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .ad-test-container {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #333;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .ad-container {
        margin: 2rem 0;
        padding: 1rem;
        border: 1px dashed #ccc;
        border-radius: 4px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }

    .article-content {
        margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .instructions {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding: 1rem;
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        border-left: 4px solid #666;
    }
</style>
